**Negotiation Strategy:**

**1. Opening Position (Buyer Requests)**:
- Risk assessment escrow: $200,000 (48-month release if no OCR penalties)
- Encryption breach escrow: $100,000 (72-month release if no device breaches)
- BAA gap escrow: $75,000 (24-month release if all BAAs executed)
- EMR data migration: 100% Seller-borne costs
